data.description: Turn back time. Relax on your front porch & enjoy watching beautiful sunsets + the occasional equestrian ride by. Unwind with the park-like expanse of lawn & shade trees. Prolific gardening can be had here with the rich soil & savor the fruit from the apple-cherry-Italian plum-pear trees + elderberries. Island kitchen w/2021 remodeling. November 2021 new roof (old one stripped off). Cozy Blaze King stove w/new tile surround. MF laundry, remodeled bathrooms, 20x20 "studio" can be used for an office, school room, workout room, etc.  24x30 building can be used as a shop, barn or combination of both. "Carport" w/room for 2 vehicles. Great pastureland for horses, cows, etc. Quick easy mostly paved access to shopping/services in Spokane, Spokane Valley, and be on Coeur d'Alene Lake in about 25 minutes. Noted Freeman School District w/school bus service--possibly even at your driveway.
